{"tid":1013291,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱去拜年俾親戚兜巴星","createTime":"2019-02-08T08:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T13:58:57.000Z","uid":5077,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60a018e1fad0f5ac04eade37e102958b038ef1b8","tid":1013291,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱去親戚屋企拜年，<br />\n咁啱屋企播緊尋晚山東老撚對鳥棲場波，<br />\n見到鳥棲輸咗忍唔住唉咗一聲，<br />\n俾個老嘢聽到，佢就屌：<br />\n「你唉乜嘢？你都係中國人嚟㗎！」<br />\n我笑咗笑，話我已經入咗日本藉，<br />\n仲改咗個名叫犬養學富<br />\n<br />\n之後就發現原來有個表哥<br />\n全程瞪大對眼揸實拳頭好似想打我咁<br />\n咁啱我呢排bulk緊，身型有啲似bane，<br />\n佢淆淆地先無咁放肆<br />\n<br />\n嘻，中國人？我呸！"},{"pid":"ee4f7a6205ba262f0e0015b5fb1eb93b1a715a90","tid":1013291,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"a03634d61522e6b05562475d219e5ccca370b4c5","tid":1013291,"uid":194877,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"-10/10"},{"pid":"0029fe7075f20074ad3418d7f27ea7f0d12d4bf6","tid":1013291,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"笑都笑唔出。<br />\n<br />\n0.1/10"},{"pid":"96df751c405db2c0ffeac94e5c71ab4b6bdb3ea8","tid":1013291,"uid":229883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"淨講on9你有滿分"},{"pid":"872def978c21740e3cd6a28a9d22f65ae762bc7d","tid":1013291,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"你表哥冇腹肌先淆你姐"},{"pid":"c42d8697db4f901d9107c6e80207c5e0e43be22b","tid":1013291,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"笑甚麼笑 你也是支那人"},{"pid":"8e2d8af4f5d11de15e0f701440461db3c9cc8bf2","tid":1013291,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"邊到兜巴星？"},{"pid":"5541245934d0a51405b90deac0a641a97e199fab","tid":1013291,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote